title: Supreme Court hears case on lawsuits against public officials for blocking users on social media
description: The Supreme Court is hearing oral arguments in two cases involving public officials blocking someone on social media and whether it violates free speech rights. NBC News’ Laura Jarrett outlines the cases in question and how the justices may rule.

title: Hamas could inspire attacks in the U.S., FBI chief Christopher Wray says
description: FBI Director Christopher Wray warned Hamas' actions in the Middle East could inspire terrorist attacks, including by violent extremists in the U.S.
